  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By-- the first location, Arkhangelsk, was just a, a point--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--where they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people were coming in from every-- each direction.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Over there, they are sorting up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they see 25 years, in 5 years, I, I don't have to-- I have no right to live close to a big city.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In 10 years, I don't have the right to vote.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's practically, like, 40 years they give me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This kind of-- type of people-- they don't want to read exactly details.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm not a dangerous person.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No, they put in right away signature, uh-huh, Kolyma, Kolyma, Kolyma.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right. they figured up I am extreme dangerous for their society.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they figure up-- they figure up-- what kind of dangerous I am?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never was a dangerous person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never kill nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- Kolyma.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What-- like I told you, over there was-- the first three months was tough.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was working [SIGHS] in bush [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very hard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a new climate for me and the food and everything take together-- a different kind of personality people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you have to live with them under one roof.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this all-- that's the environment around me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't used to this-- be a performer, actor in a different society, before a officer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And right now, if you're showing around on the underworld, different kind of people, different kind of background.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, very harsh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, like, when they put me up later, I was the editor in the local paper.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I improved my situation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was the librarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm-- I forming concerts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they was happy they had a person to organize the concerts.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
